title: StudioLinkedVST - Raptor WIN x86 VST
description:
Raptor is a standalone vst plugin for windows you can load up in your music host. Contains all of your favorite instruments that were created to mimic the sound of popular song on the radio. Raptor truly is a beast. Comes with over 208 instruments and the ability to add expansions into it will have you adding thousands of new instruments into your unit.

Instrument categories:
over 208 Modern instruments
-Bass
-Bells
-Guitars
-Hits
-Leads
-Pads
-plucks
-strings
-Drum Kits
-Drum 808s


Effects:
Reverb
Pan
Volume Gain
Release
Sustain
Glide
Voicemode-Mono,Poly,Legato
Attack
Lfo Depth
Lfo Rate
Lfo-Waveform selector,
Pitch Bend


Use Win 32 Bit Only
Recommend:5GB Free Space
